/*
 * Error Test: E3038 - len() called on a void function result
 *
 * Regression for #1490: the len() check routes void arguments
 * through reject_void_in_context so len(nothing()) catches with
 * the same E3038 the broader void-rejection framework uses.
 */

do nothing() {}

do main() {
    println(len(nothing()))
}
